- The phrase 'last month' refers to the time period between the current date and 30 days prior to it; 
- The phrase 'top 10 cities' means the 10 cities with the highest values for the average maximum temperature; 
- The phrase 'average maximum temperature' means the average of the highest temperatures recorded for each day over a given time period.

sql:
SELECT city_name
FROM cities
ORDER BY city_name;
